# ripgrep-only (NOT git): re-include the per-project repos that .gitignore hides from GIT,
# so code/content search (ripgrep, and tools built on it) still descends into them.
# Git tracking is unaffected — the sub-repos stay untracked here (they have their own remotes).
!/PiKaOs/
!/PiKaOs-docs/
!/PiKaOs-Standalone/
